headline: 1 Services Stock Worth Investigating and 2 We Brush Off
summary: Business services providers use their specialized expertise to help enterprises streamline operations and cut costs. But increasing competition from AI-driven upstarts has tempered enthusiasm, limiting the industry’s gains to 9.1% over the past six months. This return lagged the S&P 500’s 14.4% climb.
